            <h3>Environment</h3>
            
            <p>SunshinePHP Developer Conference maintains a welcoming, friendly, polite, and professional environment. Developers of all skill levels are welcome. We have a Code of Conduct that all attendees must agree to when purchasing their ticket. We take all Code of Conduct reports seriously, and our Code of Conduct will be enforced. For more information, please see <a href="/conduct">the SunshinePHP Developer Conference Code of Conduct</a>.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6 col-md-push-6">
