        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-md-pull-6">
            <h3>Arriving</h3>
            <p>Directions to the conference are located on our <a href="/venue/">Venue page</a>. When you arrive at <a href="/venue/">the Radisson Hotel Madison</a>, park in one of the lots surrounding the hotel (please do not park in front of any of the stores in the nearby strip mall. Parking is complimentary.</p>
            
            <p>Enter the front doors under the awning at the front of the hotel, proceed through the lobby, and turn left. You will see a registration table with the red Madison PHP logo on the front of it. Check in at this table.</p>
            
            <h3>Getting Help</h3>
            
            <p>If you need assistance at any time, any one of <a href="/organizers/">our organizers</a> would be happy to help you out. The organizers will be moving around the venue, but the easiest place to find them will be at the registration table (with the red Madison PHP logo on the front of it).</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    
