            <h3>Talks</h3>
            
            <p>The rooms for the talks will be to the right and left of the registration area. Each talk room will be clearly labeled on the schedule. If you have any questions about which room a certain talk is in, stop by the registration table.</p>
            
            <p>Our goal is to have the chairs set at tables to make it easy to take notes and/or follow along on a laptop. This may not always be possible, but we will be working to ensure as many chairs have table space as possible.</p>
            
            <p>The talks will be accompanied by slides projected on large screens at the front of the room. The largest room will have two screens. The speakers will have microphones.</p>
            
            <p>If you need any table or seating accomodations, visual aid, or audio assistance, please <a href="http://sunshinephp.com/contact">send us an email to let us know what you need</a>. We will do our best to assist you.</p>
        </div>
