            <h3>Food</h3>
            
            <p>Lunch will be provided on-site. If you have any dietary restrictions, please let us know when you purchase your ticket or if you have already purchased your ticket, please <a href="http://sunshinephp.com/contact">send us an email to let us know about your dietary restrictions</a>. Our caterer is happy to work with you on this. We must receive your dietary restrictions at least two weeks prior to the event for our catering requirements. If it is closer than two weeks to the event, we will do our best to accommodate you, but we may not be able to.</p>
